lib/types/candidate.ts:

export type Candidate = {
  id: string;
  project_id: string;
  location_name: string;
  address: string;
  category?: string;
  created_by: string;
  votes_agree: number;
  votes_disagree: number;
  created_at: Date;
  updated_at: Date;
};

export type CandidateVote = {
  id: string;
  candidate_id: string;
  user_id: string;
  vote_type: 'agree' | 'disagree';
  created_at: Date;
};

export type CandidateWithVotes = Candidate & {
  user_vote?: 'agree' | 'disagree' | null;
};

lib/types/index.ts에 export * from './candidate' 추가

엔드포인트:

GET /api/projects/:id/candidates
- 응답: { candidates: CandidateWithVotes[] }

POST /api/projects/:id/candidates
- 요청: { location_name, address, category }
- 응답: { id, ...candidate }
- 상태: 201

DELETE /api/projects/:id/candidates/:candidateId
- 응답: { success: true }
- 상태: 204 또는 200
- 권한: creator만 가능

POST /api/projects/:id/candidates/:candidateId/vote
- 요청: { vote_type: 'agree' | 'disagree' }
- 응답: { id, ...vote }
- 상태: 201
- 권한: 프로젝트 멤버만

구현:

1. getMarkerColor 함수 추가:
   const getMarkerColor = (candidate: CandidateWithVotes) => {
     const agree = candidate.votes_agree;
     const disagree = candidate.votes_disagree;
     const total = agree + disagree;

     if (total === 0) return '#9CA3AF'; // 회색
     const ratio = (agree / total) * 100;
     return ratio >= 66 ? '#10B981' : '#EF4444';
   };

2. 마커 렌더링 시 색상 적용:
   candidates.map((candidate) => {
     const color = getMarkerColor(candidate);
     // marker 생성 시 color 적용
   });

3. 마커 업데이트:
   - 후보지 데이터 변경 → NaverMap 재렌더링
   - 마커 색상 자동 변경

색상 정의:
- 회색: #9CA3AF (투표 없음)
- 빨강: #EF4444 (찬성 < 66%)
- 초록: #10B981 (찬성 >= 66%)
